# accessibility-change-over-time — the flagship research artifact.
# Committed:   reports/  (primary research output — 15 figures + supplementary)
# Committed:   engine-audit/  (jellycell tearsheet output for CASESTUDY App D)
# Ignored:     cache/ (MTA + ACS snapshots), artifacts/ (intermediate CSVs),
#              data/ (raw downloads), uv.lock + .venv/ (user-local).
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
uv.lock
# No trailing slash on /cache so symlinks-to-dir (e.g. reusing the
# about-the-data cache via `ln -s ../about-the-data/cache cache`) are also
# ignored — git treats symlinks-to-dir as files, not dirs.
/cache
/artifacts/
/data/
